<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>수행평가 정보</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #e0f7fa, #bbdefb);
    }
    .box {
      background: white;
      padding: 40px 60px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box">
    우리 학교 소개하기
  </div>
</body>
</html>
